<h3 style="text-align: center;">I hope your enthusiasm about skyscrapers is as great as mine! I was crazy enough to build a website about them!<br>At SkyHi, you will be able to look at a few of the tallest skyscrapers in the world and learn a few fun facts about them at the same time!<br></h3>
