<p style="text-align: center; margin-left: 250px; margin-right: 250px;">My inspiration to make this website was when I ventured out to Japan with a fellow students and professors for a winter term trip.  We visited the Tokyo Skytree and the massive size of the building has made me look at architecture more and more.  I decided that creating a website about other skyscrapers would be cool and hopefully excite you as much as it does for me.  I learned a lot about other continent's tallest skyscrapers and hope you learn just as much from visiting.  Thanks for visiting and hope you have a good time.</p>
